title: 17290 E Tennessee Dr-Aurora - Fireplace, community amenities, & more!
posting_body: ['TEXT', 'show contact info', 'NOW FOR MORE INFO!', 'Virtual tour: 17290 E Tennessee Dr', 'AREA: AURORA!', 'FEATURES:', 'Unit has a fireplace, walk-in closet, enclosed patio, and more!', 'Community features a clubhouse and tennis court!', 'INCLUDED UTILITIES:', 'Water, trash and snow removal of community areas!', 'TENANT PAID UTILITIES:', 'All other utilities paid by tenant.', 'BEDROOMS & BATHROOMS: 2 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms.', 'KITCHEN APPLIANCES INCLUDED: Stove, refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, and disposal!', 'LAUNDRY:', 'Closet laundry with electric washer and dryer.', 'FLOORING: Carpet and vinyl flooring.', 'HEAT/COOLING: Gas heat.', 'No AC.', 'PARKING: 1 assigned parking space, #143.', 'FENCING:', 'None', 'BASEMENT: No basement', 'RESTRICTIONS:', 'Pets considered with a one-time non-refundable pet fee of $250 per pet.', 'Sorry, but we cannot allow any of the following breeds of dog: American Pit Bull Terrier, American Staffordshire Terrier, and Staffordshire Bull Terrier.', 'APPLICATION FEE: $30 per adult.', 'Please note we have a 700 minimum credit score for all properties.', 'AVAILABILITY DATE: September 2nd!!', "**Applicants must be able to start a lease within 1 week of the property's listed availability date.", '**', 'LEASE TERM:', 'Initial leases are to end April through June of 2023', 'Growing marijuana inside or outside the premises is not allowed, smoking of any kind inside the property is not allowed.', 'Minimum 700 credit score required.']
